TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
That's my boss. Sorry, can't do anything about it.

Waiter, there's a golden-voiced hobo in my soup!

I have no idea what that is

Waiter, there's a portal to another dimension in my soup!

Edited February 13, 2015 by TheJewelOfJool

WE'RE TRANSCENDINGGGGG

Waiter, there's no soup in my soup!

But- wha- how- th- what?!

Waiter, there's a soggy bill in my soup!

Bill Kerman or an American form of currency? Either way, we're not responsible for any hostage holding or credit fraud.

Waiter, there's a Windows 98 in my soup!

KILL IT WITH FIRE!

Waiter, there's a Windows 8.1 in my soup!

Would you want me to upgrade it into Windows 9?

Waiter! Waiter! There's a Shine Sprite in my soup!@

I have no idea what that is and how'd you get in here, we're closed!?

Waiter, confusion is in my soup!

Ehm... what? What soup? Ah that.... what is it?

In my soup, Yoda is, waiter.

http://youtu.be/dzsnymbdxeY

Waiter, there's a red pill in my soup.

*ehm* This is your last chance. After this, there is no turning back. You call us incompetent because you've ordered the blue pill soup - the story ends. We'll take that away, give you your regular soup, and ensure you that it's *not* a green pill soup. You eat the soup - and you'll taste the greatest soup ever made, and see the world as it really is as a bonus.

And remember: All I'm offering you is a good soup, nothing less, nothing more.

Waiter, there's a klingon in my soup!

What? No... That's Bill Clinton.

Waiter, there's an eMarican president in my soup.

There's an online horse president?

Waiter, why is Ty Lee in my soup (Avatar the Last Airbender)?

Yes looks like she is hiding because of a movie failure

Waiter, why is Percy Jackson in my soup? (and he is stealing it)

That is normal, no?

Excuse me, fair worker. Why is there a hypetrain in my soup? I think I make out the numbers 1.0!

Its not real it's only a prototype at it's test drive!

Waiter, there's a knife and some cheese in my soup!!! >:-(

Then stop trying to drink with your knife! The cheese was to be had with your red wine.

Waiter, there's a telltale in my soup.

Of course there is!

Waiter, there's a robot in my soup! It's quite rude, too.

Slap it for being rude, and tell it to get back to the kitchen and make MORE BOOSTER SOUP!!!

Waiter, there is a TGV in my soup!

You did order the train station soup, right?

Waiter, there's KSP 1.0 in my soup!

Nice!

Waiter, there's a KSP forum in my soup!

*typing* Sorry, what? I was too busy posting.

Waiter, there's an amount of antimatter in my soup that's exactly equal to the amount of matter in my soup!

How is that possible? Eh, it doesn't matter. I'm sorry.

Waiter, Les Grossman is dancing in my soup.

Well, tell him to dance on the floor like a normal person!

Waiter, why is Princess Azula attacking my soup? (I know, another Avatar: The Last Airbender reference)

let me fix that *vaporizes*

waiter, there's a Duna in my soup
